{"tid":2489457,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我做飲食侍應，辭左辭終於屌9個店長","createTime":"2021-04-15T03:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T03:26:35.000Z","uid":111996,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4df493de30bf1cef6308dddebf638f5d5804c201","tid":2489457,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"記得第一日返工，佢已經屌我點點點，我為左錢忍左佢好耐，返左半年有D錢咁咪辭職，仲講明叫我搵工當無做過呢份工。<br />\n<br />\n辭左職開頭幾日終於唔煩我以為可以好地地走，點知佢又發癲。 <br />\n果一日屌佢果日對白是咁的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：ME. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />店長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：幫我果到拎野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：果到姐係邊到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係你屋企呀屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：....我都辭左職啦仲想我點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：辭左職大哂呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母你走啦，返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好呀！我而家走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好呀，記得賠錢走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：賠乜錢走呀，而家係你叫我走架喎，個個都聽到，同事又聽到，客人又聽到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你而家做嘢囉（自己走撚左出鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n平時搵我做出氣筒，我駁嘴，佢開始癲到客人都搞<br />\n<br />\n有一日，4個學生排緊隊，開頭無咩位置佢地2個，2個咁坐。無幾耐應該幾分鐘後有食客走，佢要求調位4位一齊坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />店長   ，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食客 ，廚房同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你地係唔係要調呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地要調D野食重新排隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.....得啦得啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講，佢果D單重新排隊做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手頭上無單喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等15分鐘先做佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...（驚左佢）<br />\n<br />\n真係大概15分鐘後先整野食比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨天返夜，聽講中午個店長屌9 個食客，食客屌返佢，大概我唔知發生咩事....."},{"pid":"33b87a411f6dd1e3ca8dbc3fc8ceb5370e2e0cc6","tid":2489457,"uid":237893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:15:32.000Z","msg":"開名?"},{"pid":"12facb393756c16a205c911b15ef982e207ff40d","tid":2489457,"uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:16:54.000Z","msg":"去做食客<br />\n然後玩鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1390c237d40e47b53cf12ee839198d5bc963b617","tid":2489457,"uid":111996,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"33b87a411f6dd1e3ca8dbc3fc8ceb5370e2e0cc6","tid":2489457,"uid":237893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:15:32.000Z","msg":"開名?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:17:07.000Z","msg":"霸嗎拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46667b21384c0dd9b4a80fb0b9006642494d2ecc","tid":2489457,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"想知間舖叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6264daa29584492049e1f5373ffce5f541f986a","tid":2489457,"uid":195